## Limitations

This report is based on available information as of October 2023 and may not reflect the most current developments in the CFP expansion discussions. Additionally, the perspectives included are primarily from major sports news outlets and may not encompass all stakeholder views, particularly those of smaller conferences or independent teams. Further research and stakeholder engagement would be necessary for a more comprehensive analysis.